# Keep the build context small and never leak local installs or secrets into an image.
**/node_modules
**/.svelte-kit
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# Secrets + local state must never enter an image (compose injects env at run time).
.env
.env.*
.run-state

# Local-only tooling + history.
.git
.github
.claude
.memory
**/*.log
